Check access to ec.europe.eu

Source: R/check_access_to_data.R
check_access_to_data.Rd

Check if R has access to resources at http://ec.europa.eu

Usage

check_access_to_data()

Value

a logical.

Author

Markus Kainu markus.kainu@kapsi.fi

Examples

# \donttest{
check_access_to_data()
#> [1] TRUE
# }
